Perhaps we have not yet achieved a Chateau Lafite- Rothschild, a Montrachet or a Musigny, but we are well on our way. It may take another generation, but knowledge, dedi- cation, trial-and-error will move us closer to the ultimate of perfection.

In the interval, it is our responsibility to bring you the best of northern California and New York State. Each wine listed below has been tasted intrinsically and comparatively. Each is best within class. If you are interested in experiencing what the vineyards of America have to offer, the selections below will bring you this possibility. For those who want to learn, there is much adventure and knowledge to be gained. Happy comparative tasting!
